oai_dc:dc.dc:title: The dispersal of Culicoides brevitarsis in eastern New South Wales and associations with the occurrences of arbovirus infections in cattle

Barchia, I. M.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Culicoides brevitarsis

oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Distributions of the vector Culicoides brevitarsis Kieffer (Diptera: Ceratopogonidae) (determined from light trap data) and 2 arboviruses (determined from seroconversions in sentinel cattle) were studied in eastern New South Wales in 1993-94. Full article published in Veterinary Record (1996); 73, 174-178
